      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) represents a mechanically sound example of the legendary S54 platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features six individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline, delivering linear power through a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive Vanos overhaul and a reinforced rear subframe, addressing the primary structural concerns of the chassis. The suspension retains its factory-spec geometry with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the M Variable Differential Lock provides optimal traction through the corners. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the car exhibits honest patina consistent with its mileage while maintaining exceptional mechanical integrity. A driver-focused machine with no deferred maintenance.",
